Police in Mbooni West, Makueni, are investigating the death of a two-year-old boy who allegedly committed suicide on Tuesday evening. Area Chief Richard Ndisya said the body was found by his mother dangling from a rafter with a rope round the neck. The mother said she was away when the incident occurred. Speaking to the Star on the phone, the chief said the death is suspicious, considering his age. He said police are investigating. Efforts to reach Mbooni West police boss James Barasa were unsuccessful.